WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.849 --> 00:00:01.849
 Hello! 

00:00:01.849 --> 00:00:04.720
 I offer a recipe for lazy pizza. Lazy because 

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:08.109
 it is done very quickly and it turns out super tasty. 

00:00:08.109 --> 00:00:12.350
 such products will be needed. Four buns, two onions, two 

00:00:12.350 --> 00:00:16.770
 Tomatoes, 150 g of mushrooms, 150 g of hard cheese, vegetable 

00:00:16.770 --> 00:00:23.390
 oil and salt, pepper to taste. Each bun is cut in half. Remove 

00:00:23.390 --> 00:00:42.069
 crumb. Onion chop finely. Mushrooms in small pieces. Tomatoes 

00:00:42.069 --> 00:00:51.640
 cut into cubes. Onion fry on vegetable 

00:00:51.640 --> 00:00:58.690
 oil until golden brown. Add mushrooms, salt, pepper. Fry 

00:00:58.690 --> 00:01:26.350
 until ready. Now we mix all the ingredients. 

00:01:26.350 --> 00:01:31.329
 spread on buns and cover with cheese, chopped 

00:01:31.329 --> 00:01:46.060
 Recipes. Microwave Ready until 

00:01:46.060 --> 00:01:53.539
 the cheese will melt, which is about 5-7 minutes. 

00:01:53.539 --> 00:01:55.050
 Everything is very simple. 

00:01:55.050 --> 00:01:56.049
 Enjoy your meal. 

